🔐 Security Design
Tamper Prevention
If backend data is altered:
Recomputed hash ≠ on-chain hash
Verification fails
If NFC URL is copied:
Ownership & metadata still validated on-chain
If NFT is transferred:
Ownership reflects real-time wallet holder

📡 API Endpoints
Method	Endpoint	Purpose
GET	/api/product/:id	Fetch product
GET	/api/transfers/:id	Fetch transfer history
POST	/api/mint	Store new product
POST	/api/transfer	Log ownership transfer
POST	/api/scan	Log verification event
GET	/api/products/:wallet	Manufacturer dashboard

📱 NFC Implementation
NFC Tag contains:
https://tag-in-rift.vercel.app/v/<assetId>
Requirements:
HTTPS deployment
Public URL
URL record format
Supported:
Android

iPhone (background NFC URL reading)
